node.title: Auckland street surrounded by police amid 'serious incident'
node.description: Police officers remain at the scene.
node.content: ["A street has been cordoned off in Auckland's Flat Bush overnight amid what's being described as a \"serious incident\".\n", "Police say officers remain at the scene in Bezar Pl on Sunday morning.", "The armed offenders squad was also at the scene, a resident told the NZ Herald.", "Cordons are in place in the Bezar Pl area, police said in a statement.", "No further details are currently available.", "More to come."]
